  * Got a new logo (actually the same but simplified).
  * Removed hardcoded list of builders.
  * Minor bugs fixed.

0.1 (04 Dec 2010)

  * Initial version.
  * Check status of the last build for the core buildbots only.
  * Check extra details through the web browser.
